        <div class="comment">
            <h3>
                <span class="comment-vote">
                    <span id="c-546520701" class="vote-count">0</span>
                        <a href="javascript:;" id="btn-546520701" class="j a_show_login" data-cid="546520701">有用</a>
                </span>
                <span class="comment-info">
                    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/zishuzishu/">紫书</a>
                        <span class="user-stars allstar50 rating" title="力荐"></span>
                    <span>2012-07-22</span>
                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">    非常值得一看，几乎字字真言。。。。。。不由得让我想起六祖来，当年解坛经，也是舌灿莲花。当已经得到道的时候，语言之技便无意中达到了顶峰。</p>
        </div>
    </li>

        </ul>
</div>

        

