            <div class="reading-note" data-cid="19619894">
              <div class="short">
                
                  <span class="">
If you don't know how to be silent, it becomes heavy. It is not that by saying things you communicate --no. It is by saying things that you unburden yourself. In fact, through words communication is not possible;just the opposite is possible -- you can avoid communication. You can talk, and you can create a screen of words around you so that your real situation cannot be known by others. You clo...</span>
                  &nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/19619894/">(<span class="">3回应</span>)</a>
                <p class="pl">
                  <span class="">2012-07-13 11:50</span>
                  
                    &nbsp;&nbsp;<span class="">2人喜欢</span>
                </p>
              </div>
              <div class="all hidden" style="display:none" >
                
If you don't know how to be silent, it becomes heavy. It is not that by saying things you communicate --no. It is by saying things that you unburden yourself. In fact, through words communication is not possible;just the opposite is possible -- you can avoid communication. You can talk, and you can create a screen of words around you so that your real situation cannot be known by others. You clothe yourself through words.
                  <div class="col-rec-con clearfix">
                    







