            <div class="reading-note" data-cid="19619460">
              <div class="short">
                
                  <span class="">   When you try to understand Lao Tzu he zigzags. Sometimes you see him going towards the east and   sometimes towards the west, because he says east is west and west is east, they are together, they are one.


He believes in the unity of the opposites. And that is how life is.So Lao Tzu is just a spokesman of life. If life is absurd, Lao Tzu is absurd; if life has an absurd logic to
it, Lao T...</span>
                  &nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/19619460/">(<span class="">1回应</span>)</a>
